messages.message: Idk what the right place to post this is or to find out about known issues, but I get an issue trying to load this .ibrefiner on prod https://www.instabase.com/apps/refiner-v5/edit/ib_sales/sales-demo/fs/Instabase%20Drive/big-hank-bank/prog/refiner5.ibrefiner , some other refiners seem to work ok, so I’m not sure how to go about debugging this issue. This is the same refiner as what’s broken for me in UAT, so that’s making it hard for us to determine if it’s a bug that needs to be fixed and cherry picked into the June release or not.
